'''Johann Sebastian Bach''' (* wazaka 21. <span>Marichi</span> <sup>Jul.</sup> <span>/</span> <span style="margin-left:-.1em">31</span> <span style="margin-left:-.1em">Marichi&nbsp;1685 <sup>greg.</sup></span> ku Eisenach, Saxony-Eisenach ; † 28. July 1750 mu Leipzig, Kursachsen) anali woyimba wamkulu waku [[Germany]] munthawi ya Baroque. Bach amadziwika kuti ndi m'modzi mwa oimba wofunikira kwambiri ku Europe. Adakopa oyimba pambuyo pake monga Mozart, Beethoven ndi Brahms, komanso adaimba nyimbo zambiri. Kupanga kwa Bach ndi chimodzi mwazabwino kwambiri m'mbiri ya nyimbo.

Bach adabadwira ku Eisenach mu 1685. Adaphunzitsidwa kusewera zeze ndi bambo ake, a Johann Ambrosius, woliza lipenga kukhothi potumikira Kalonga wa Eisenach. Bach anali asanakwanitse zaka khumi bambo ake atamwalira, ndikumusiya wamasiye. Anapita kukakhala kunyumba kwa mchimwene wake; mchimwene wake amakhala ku Ohrdruf. Chifukwa cha liwu lake labwino, Bach adapeza ntchito ku nyumba ya amonke ya Michaelis ku Lüneberg mu 1700. Liwu lake lidasintha kanthawi pang'ono, koma adapitiliza kuyimba. Atagwira ntchito kwakanthawi ku Weimar mu 1703 ngati woyimba zeze, Bach adakhala katswiri ku Neue Kirche ku Arnstadt (1703-1707). Ubwenzi wake ndi khonsolo yamatchalitchi udali wovuta popeza woimbayo wachinyamata nthawi zambiri ankanyalanyaza udindo wake, posankha kuyimba limba. Nkhani ina imafotokoza za tchuthi cha miyezi inayi chomwe adapatsa Bach, kuti apite ku Lubeck komwe akadziwitse nyimbo za Dietrich Buxtehude. Anabwerera ku Arnstadt patatha nthawi yayitali akuyembekezereka, akwiyitsa bungweli. Kenako adatumikira mwachidule ku St. Blasius ku Mühlhausen ngati oyimba, kuyambira mu Juni 1707, ndipo adakwatira msuweni wake, Maria Barbara Bach, nthawi yophukira ija. Bach analemba Toccata yake yotchuka ndi Fugue mu D minor (BWV 565) ndi ma cantata ake oyamba ali ku Mühlhausen. Kenako adagwira ntchito kwa a Duke of Sachsen-Weimar mu 1708, akugwira ntchito yoyimba milandu ndikuimba mu orchestra, pomalizira pake adakhala mtsogoleri wawo mu 1714. Adalemba nyimbo zingapo nthawi imeneyi, kuphatikiza Orgel-Büchlein. Bach adachoka ku Weimar ndipo adapeza ntchito mu Disembala 1717 ngati Kapellmeister ku Cöthen. Mu 1720, mkazi wa Bach adamwalira mwadzidzidzi, ndikumusiya ndi ana anayi (ena atatu adamwalira ali aang'ono). Posakhalitsa, adakumana ndi mkazi wake wachiwiri, Anna Magdalena Wilcke, yemwe adakwatirana naye mu Disembala 1721. Adzabala ana 13, ngakhale asanu okha ndi omwe adzapulumuke ali mwana. Zisanu ndi chimodzi Brandenburg Concertos (BWV 1046-51), mwazinthu zina zambiri zothandizidwa, kuyambira zaka zake za Cöthen. Bach adakhala Kantor wa Thomas School ku Leipzig mu Meyi 1723 ndipo adagwira ntchitoyi mpaka kumwalira kwake. Anali ku Leipzig komwe adapanga ma cantata ake ambiri. Bach pamapeto pake sanakhutire ndi ntchitoyi, osati chifukwa chopeza ndalama zochepa, komanso chifukwa chantchito zovuta komanso zida zoyipa. Chifukwa chake, adalandira ntchito zina, kuphatikiza kuyang'anira mzinda wa Collegium Musicum, gulu la akatswiri oimba komanso akatswiri ochita masewera olimbitsa thupi omwe amapatsa makonsati sabata iliyonse, mu 1729. Anakhalanso woyang'anira nyimbo ku Dresden Court mu 1736, potumikira Frederick Augustus II. Ngakhale anali ndi ntchito zochepa, adapatsidwa ufulu wolemba zomwe akufuna. Bach adayamba ulendo wopita ku Berlin m'ma 1740, osati chifukwa mwana wake, Carl Philipp Emanuel, anali woyimba kumeneko. Odwala matenda ashuga, Bach adamwalira pa Julayi 28, 1750.
